iOS 7.0 API Diffs

PDF Companion File

    iOS 6.1 to iOS 7.0 API Differences

    Added frameworks:

    • GameController
    • JavaScriptCore
    • MediaAccessibility
    • MultipeerConnectivity
    • SafariServices
    • SpriteKit
